模拟卡方测验

Document Author

2016-12-17

  • 1 编写投掷120次计算x-squared值
  • 2 重复两万次
  • 3 我们可以来看一下这个渐变的过程

说明：一个质地均匀的骰子，投120次用卡方检验得到X-squared值，重复20000次得到20000个w值画出卡方图，然后在做一条自由度为5的卡方分布拟合曲线

1 编写投掷120次计算x-squared值

# 一般思维的函数
thow1 <- function(times=120){
  n <- 0
  df <- data.frame(dice=1:6,times=0)#创造一个df记录这些骰子的结果
  while (n<=times) {
    dice <- sample.int(6, size = 1, replace =T)#投一次骰子
    #避免多重If语句
    index <- which(df$dice==dice)
    df[index,"times"] <- df[index,"times"]+1
    n <- n+1
  }
  Xsquared <- sum( (df$times-times/6)^2/(times/6) )#chi
  return(list(df=df,chisuq=Xsquared))
}
# 直接利用sample函数进行模拟
thow2 <- function(times=120){
  dice <- sample.int(6,size = times,replace = T)
  table <- table(dice)
  df <- as.data.frame(table)
  Xsquared <- sum( (df$Freq-times/6)^2/(times/6) )#chi
  return(list(df=df,chisuq=Xsquared))
  #这样就避免了 显式 的循环
}

2 重复两万次

repeatThow <- function( repeated=20000){
  values <- thow2()$chisuq
  for (i in 1:(repeated-1)) {
    value <- thow2()$chisuq
    values <- append(values,value)
  }
  return(values)
}
#绘制模拟的结果
result <- repeatThow()
plot(density(result,bw = 0.2))
#绘制理论卡方分布
x <- pretty(c(0,33),50)
y <- dchisq(x,df=5)
points(x,y,
     type = "l",
     xlab = "chisq values",
     ylab = "density",
     col="red")
legend("topright",c("empirical","theoretical"),lty = 1,col = 1:2)

3 我们可以来看一下这个渐变的过程

for (i in c(100,500,10000,20000,50000)) {
  #绘制模拟的结果
  result <- repeatThow(repeated = i)
  plot(density(result,bw = 0.2),main=paste0(i,"\'s repeat"))
  #绘制理论卡方分布
  x <- pretty(c(0,33),50)
  y <- dchisq(x,df=5)
  points(x,y,
       type = "l",
       xlab = "chisq values",
       ylab = "density",
       col="red")
  legend("topright",c("empirical","theoretical"),lty = 1,col = 1:2)
}
